{"word":"δαψιλής","slug":"δαψιλής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δαψιλής</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δάπτω'><el>δάπτω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>abundant, plentiful</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:— <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-έως</el>, <i>in abundance</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of persons, <i>liberal, profuse</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <el>δαψιλέστατα ζῆν</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}